📈 Stock Analysis & AI Investment Advisor 💡
This project is a Streamlit-powered investment dashboard that helps users analyze stock data and receive AI-generated investment insights — all in one clean, interactive interface.

🚀 Features:
🔍 Real-time stock price fetching (Indian & global) using Yahoo Finance and Alpha Vantage APIs.

📊 Volatility (risk) and expected return analysis using historical data.

📁 Portfolio-level insights, including Sharpe ratio calculations.

🤖 AI-driven investment suggestions via Google Gemini API, tailored to user portfolio characteristics.

🧠 Custom AI Q&A: Ask your own finance questions and get intelligent responses.

⚙️ Tech Stack:
Python (Streamlit, NumPy, Requests)

APIs: Alpha Vantage, Yahoo Finance, Google Gemini

Deployed as a responsive web app with rich UX styling

⚠️ Disclaimer: This tool is for educational and informational purposes only. Not financial advice.

